item.title: Nine Dutch Guys Bring the Heat to Blustery Camden
item.author: Tobi Ampapa,
item.description: Jungle By Night may not be a name on everyone’s radar - but they more than should be. The nine-piece instrumental collective, hailing from Amsterdam, has a sound that lies somewhere in the middle of jazz, afrobeat (I’m talking your uncle’s favourite Fela) and funk.
